# Generated novel outputs — products are fully rebuildable from source + pinned code,
# so the entire tree is ignored. Authoritative evidence summaries live tracked under
# docs/evidence/. Only output/README.md (the convention doc) is committed.
output/*
!output/README.md

# In-source generated outputs: src/output/ 是可重建产物而非源码;
# 上面的 output/* 锚定根目录,挡不住 src 下同名树,这里单独补一条。
src/output/

# 散落的一次性任务/中间产物(撤跟踪保留本地,可重新生成或一次性使用)
